  "text": [
    "I hunted heaven",
    "for him.",
    "No dice.",
    "Too uppity,",
    "it was. Not enough",
    "music, or dark dirt.",
    "I begged the earth empty",
    "of him. Death",
    "believes in us whether",
    "we believe",
    "or not. For a long while",
    "I watch the sound",
    "of a boy bouncing a ball",
    "down the block",
    "take its time",
    "to reach me. Father,",
    "find me when",
    "you want. I\u2019ll wait."
  ],
  "title": "Piet\u00e0",
  "year": ""
